text: qRRT - PCR positive samples were further titrated to evaluate the infectivity of the virus . On days 4 and 6 pi , we recorded positive TCID 50 values in the oviduct of 43 % of the birds , while the organs of the respiratory and digestive tracts were positive in 50 % and 25 % of the birds respectively , only on day 4 pi ( Table 1 and Figure 2 ) . We did not observe cytopathic effects culturing kidney , brain and spleen samples .
